## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ed5cd-135">"Default"에 자동으로 할당은 일련은 디자인 타임 및 런타임 모두에 추가 되 면 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea> 개체 또는 첫 번째 사용 가능한 차트 영역에는 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartAreaCollection> "Default" 존재 하지 않는 경우.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed5cd-135">When a series is added at both design time and run time, it is automatically assigned to the "Default" <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea> object, or the first available chart area in the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartAreaCollection> if "Default" does not exist.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ed5cd-136">계열을 그릴 수에 하지 않을 경우 길이가 0 인 문자열을이 속성을 설정 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed5cd-136">Set this property to a zero-length string if you do not want the series to be plotted.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```vb  
' Create a new legend and associate three series with the legend.  
Public Sub CreateSecondLegend()  
    ' Attach the first series to a chart area.  
    Chart1.Series["Series1"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 1";  
  
    ' Attach the second series to a chart area.  
    Chart1.Series["Series2"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 2";  
  
End Sub 'CreateSecondLegend  
```  
  
```csharp  
// Create a new legend and associate three series with the legend.  
public void CreateSecondLegend()  
{  
     // Attach the first series to a chart area.  
     Chart1.Series["Series1"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 1";  
  
     // Attach the second series to a chart area.  
     Chart1.Series["Series2"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 2";  
  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ed5cd-220">유효한 ARGB (알파, 빨간색, 녹색, 파랑) 값으로 될 수 있는 일련의 그림자 색을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed5cd-220">Gets or sets the shadow color of a series, which can be to any valid ARGB (alpha, red, green, blue) value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ed5cd-221">알파 값; 현실적인 그림자 효과 얻을 데 사용할 수 있습니다. 그림자의 "128,0,0,0"의 색상 값을 사용해 보십시오.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed5cd-221">The alpha value can be used to achieve a realistic shadow effect; try using a color value of "128,0,0,0" for shadows.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ed5cd-222">그림자를 구현 하려면 설정는 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.ShadowOffset%2A> 영 (0)이 아닌 값으로 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed5cd-222">To implement a shadow, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.ShadowOffset%2A> property to a value other than zero (0).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```  
' Set series shadow color and offset  
Public Sub SetSeriesShadow()  
     Chart1.Series("Default"}.ShadowColor = Color.Blue  
     Chart1.Series("Default"}.ShadowOffset = 2  
End Sub 'SetSeriesShadow  
```  
  
```csharp  
// Set series shadow color and offset   
public void SetSeriesShadow()  
{      
    Chart1.Series("Default"}.ShadowColor = Color.Blue;  
    Chart1.Series["Default"].ShadowOffset = 2;  
}  
```
